Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.25,1:05:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}很忠实\N{\fs60} loyal.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.65,1:05:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}虽然我有在外逢场作戏\N{\fs60}Despite the other women...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.09,1:05:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}但每次做爱\N{\fs60}I always made love to Ava
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.58,1:05:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我都把她当成我唯一的女人\N{\fs60}as if she was the only one.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.19,1:05:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我不是说生意都很顺利\N{\fs60}I'm not saying I didn't have setbacks.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.26,1:05:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}没有枪子儿跑得快\N{\fs60}It's not called gunrunning for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.43,1:05:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}怎能叫军火贩子\N{\fs60}You gotta be fast on your feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.20,1:05:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}有时军火还没运到 革命战争就已经爆发了\N{\fs60}Some revolutions blow over the guns even get there.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.45,1:05:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}对我们来说和平比什么代价都大\N{\fs60}There's nothing's more expensive for an arms dealer than peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.51,1:05:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}协议停火？停火是什么意思？\N{\fs60}Truce? What do you mean, truce?
