Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.93,1:07:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}没事？\N{\fs60}Nothing?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.28,1:07:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我爱你\N{\fs60}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.74,1:07:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我也爱你\N{\fs60}I love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.79,1:07:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}长官\N{\fs60}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.00,1:08:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我现在是最好的，还活着的死亡军火贩\N{\fs60}I was now the best merchant of death alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.39,1:08:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}虽然我没有一架私人飞机 但我有一整队飞机\N{\fs60}I didn't own my own plane, I owned a fleet.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.09,1:08:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我每周至少一次运货去利比里亚，拉利昂和象牙海岸\N{\fs60}Running guns into Liberia, Sierra Leone, or the lvory Coast at least once a week.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.91,1:08:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}大部分时间我使用假证件\N{\fs60}Most trips I had phony paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.30,1:08:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}如果赶时间\N{\fs60}The deadline was tight
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.72,1:08:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我就只有冒险\N{\fs60}and I had to cut corners,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.99,1:08:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}干脆简单到连证件也省了\N{\fs60}I had no paperwork at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.37,1:08:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我也不担心\N{\fs60}But I wasn't overly concerned.
