Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.75,1:14:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}这个我不那么肯定\N{\fs60}I'm not as certain.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.68,1:14:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}起来\N{\fs60}All right, get up.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.54,1:14:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}罪名是？\N{\fs60}What's the charge?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.47,1:14:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你在塞拉利昂干嘛？\N{\fs60}What are you doing in Sierra Leone...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.98,1:14:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}狩猎旅行\N{\fs60}I'm on safari.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.18,1:14:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}是吗？猎野兽？\N{\fs60}Yeah? You're hunting wildebeests
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.56,1:14:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}用机关枪？\N{\fs60}with a submachine gun?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.64,1:14:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你也替公园管理局工作？\N{\fs60}Do you also work with the Park Service?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.64,1:14:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我的罪名是无照狩猎吗？\N{\fs60}Hunting without a license, is that the charge?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.95,1:15:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}装什么傻？\N{\fs60}Why are we playing games?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.87,1:15:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你私运军火\N{\fs60}You traffic arms.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.53,1:15:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}是买卖\N{\fs60}Trade.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.29,1:15:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}买卖就是私运\N{\fs60}Trade. Traffic.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.46,1:15:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你提供世上最穷的人们\N{\fs60}You get rich by giving the poorest people on the planet
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.36,1:15:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}互相屠杀的工具以此致富\N{\fs60}the means to continue killing each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.16,1:15:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你知道我为什么做这个\N{\fs60}Do you konw why I do what I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.85,1:15:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我能选择其他更荣耀的任务\N{\fs60} I mean, there are more prestigious assignments.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.79,1:15:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}比方追查核武\N{\fs60}Keeping track of nuclear arsenals,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.04,1:15:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你认为那对世界和平更重要？\N{\fs60}You'd think that's more critical to world security,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.02,1:15:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}不对！\N{\fs60}but it's not.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.02,1:15:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}今天十个战争受害者中有九人\N{\fs60}No, nine out of ten war victims today
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.38,1:15:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}是死于攻击性来福枪和小型武器 正如你的商品\N{\fs60}are killed with assault rifles and small like yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.95,1:15:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}那些核飞弹？\N{\fs60}Those nuclear missiles?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.97,1:15:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}它们还在发射筒里坐着呢\N{\fs60}They sit in their silos.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.12,1:15:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你的AK-47才是大规模杀伤性武器\N{\fs60}Your AK-47? That is the real weapon of mass destruction.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.80,1:15:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}瓦伦丁特工，我不想害死人\N{\fs60}I don't want people dead, Agent Valentine.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.54,1:15:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我没拿枪指着别人的脑袋要他开枪\N{\fs60}I don't put a gun to anybody's head and make them shoot.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.67,1:15:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我是说，他开一枪，对我的生意有好处\N{\fs60}I admit, but shooting war is better for business,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.56,1:15:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}但我希望人们使用我的枪但不打死人\N{\fs60}but I prefer people to fire my guns and miss.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.93,1:15:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}只要他们开枪就行\N{\fs60}Just as long as they're firing.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.05,1:15:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我能走了吗？\N{\fs60}Can I go now?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.60,1:16:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我身上没有你想要的 除了手铐之外\N{\fs60}You've got nothing on me. Except cuffs.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.34,1:16:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}既然你要讲法\N{\fs60}Since you're so concerned with the law,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.65,1:16:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}那你一定知道\N{\fs60}you must know that I'm legally
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.73,1:16:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我能合法的拘留你24小时而不起诉你\N{\fs60}permitted to hold you for twenty-four hours without charging you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.42,1:16:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}或许你会问，我为什么要这么做\N{\fs60}You might ask why I would do that and I can assure you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.38,1:16:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我保证不是因为我喜欢你陪我\N{\fs60}It's not because I enjoy your company, because I don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.95,1:16:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}原因是在许可的24小时内\N{\fs60}No, the reason why I'll delay you for every second
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.61,1:16:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我要居留你每一秒钟\N{\fs60}of the permissible twenty-four hours
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.58,1:16:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我就拖延了你的致命武器去杀人\N{\fs60}Is I'm delaying your deadly trade and the deaths of your victims.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.84,1:16:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我不认为我拿了你一天\N{\fs60}I don't think of it as taking a day from you...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.78,1:16:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}而是多给他们一天\N{\fs60}...but giving a day to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.70,1:16:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}因为你不自由\N{\fs60}Some innocent man, woman, or child
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.99,1:16:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}所以世上那些无辜的平民才能多活一天\N{\fs60} is going to have an extra day on this earth because you're not free.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.69,1:16:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}所以...23小时55分钟后...\N{\fs60}So, I will see you in twenty-three hours
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.15,1:16:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我会再来\N{\fs60}and fifty-five minutes, hm?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.37,1:16:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}瓦伦丁知道他不必守着我\N{\fs60}Valentine knew he didn't have to guard me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.75,1:16:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我也没地方可逃\N{\fs60}There was nowhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.23,1:17:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}或许他希望当地人会把我分尸\N{\fs60}Or maybe he was hoping the locals would tear me apart.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.77,1:17:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}但他们忙着玩我的飞机\N{\fs60}But they were too busy with the plane.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.65,1:17:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}就像停了一辆好车在纽约布朗区\N{\fs60}It's like parking your car in certain neighborhoods in the Bronx.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.55,1:17:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你绝对不会这么做\N{\fs60}You just don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.71,1:17:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}以我的观点来看\N{\fs60}The way I looked at it
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.08,1:17:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}这只是非洲的自然现象 或是生命的自然现象\N{\fs60}it's the way of Africa, maybe life.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.91,1:17:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}所有从自然来的东西最后终将回归自然\N{\fs60}Everything that comes from the earth eventually returns.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.75,1:17:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}即使40吨的安通纳12型货机也一样\N{\fs60}Even a 40-ton Atonov-12 cargo plane.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.18,1:18:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我的礼物，给你\N{\fs60}A gift. For you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.42,1:18:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}还好你及时到了\N{\fs60}You know, you've arrived just in time.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.86,1:18:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我担心他在你来之前就死了\N{\fs60}I was afraid that he might die
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.02,1:18:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你就没机会了宰了他\N{\fs60}before you got your chance to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.86,1:18:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}这个人...来此...想取代你\N{\fs60}This man came here hoping to take your place.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.66,1:19:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我说的对吧？\N{\fs60}Is that not so?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.96,1:19:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}不，我不是来为巴提斯先生提供武器的\N{\fs60}No, I'm not here to supply Mr. Baptiste.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.31,1:19:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我是来给他的敌人提供武器的\N{\fs60}I am here to supply his enemies.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.54,1:19:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我想这笔交易我已经无法完成了\N{\fs60}I fear it's a sale I shall never complete.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.56,1:19:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}他杀了你一个亲人...你叔叔...\N{\fs60}He killed your blood... Your uncle...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.42,1:19:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}他本来想杀你的\N{\fs60}when he tried to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.29,1:19:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}不要\N{\fs60}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.90,1:19:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}不要？\N{\fs60}No?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.65,1:19:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你要我就放了他？\N{\fs60}You want that I should let him go?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.17,1:19:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}“不，我...”\N{\fs60}"No. I..."
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.50,1:20:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你的确想要他死\N{\fs60}You do want him dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.37,1:20:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}只是...\N{\fs60}You just...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.16,1:20:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}不想亲自动手\N{\fs60}don't want to have to do it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.03,1:20:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}好\N{\fs60}So.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.01,1:20:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我们一起来\N{\fs60}We will do this together.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.38,1:20:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}这将是我们结合的经验\N{\fs60}This will be a bonding experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.38,1:20:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你知道，只要你想，随时可以住手\N{\fs60}You know you can stop this any time that you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.57,1:20:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}但我不认为你想\N{\fs60}But I don't think that you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.95,1:20:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}一句话就好\N{\fs60}Just say the word.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.86,1:20:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}说吧...“住手”\N{\fs60}Say it. "Stop."
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.54,1:21:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}住手\N{\fs60}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.56,1:21:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}朋友，我替你另开个房间\N{\fs60}I will get you another room, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.21,1:21:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}风景更好些的\N{\fs60}With a much nicer view.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.24,1:21:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}他帮你要了布朗-布朗，尤里先生\N{\fs60}He ordered you brown-brown, Mr. Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.56,1:21:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}什么？\N{\fs60}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.83,1:22:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}布朗-布朗\N{\fs60}Brown-brown.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.82,1:22:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}那是什么？\N{\fs60}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.06,1:22:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}海洛因\N{\fs60}A mixture of cocaine...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.38,1:22:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}和火药的混合体\N{\fs60}...and gunpowder.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.90,1:22:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}他们把它在战斗前给那些孩子们吸食\N{\fs60}They give it to the young boys before they do battle.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.13,1:22:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}吸过后他们会做任何事\N{\fs60}They'll do anything!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.60,1:22:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}下次再试吧\N{\fs60}Some other time.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.36,1:22:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我劝你还是试一下，尤里先生\N{\fs60}I suggest you try it, at least once, Mr. Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.72,1:22:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}为什么？\N{\fs60}Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.21,1:22:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}因为这是你的火药\N{\fs60}'Cause it's your gunpowder.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.32,1:22:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}在那晚之前\N{\fs60}Even before that night,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.93,1:22:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我在西非已经用过很多次毒品了\N{\fs60}I'd started doing a lot of cocaine in West Africa.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.07,1:22:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我从来没试过布朗-布朗\N{\fs60}I'd never tried brown-brown before,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.65,1:22:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}就像我从来没有杀过一个人一样\N{\fs60}but then I'd never killed a man, either.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.57,1:23:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}哦\N{\fs60}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.98,1:23:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我没做过什么吧？\N{\fs60}Oh, I didn't do anything, did I?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.77,1:23:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}{\bord0\shad4\fs75\pos(970,898)}我没做过什么吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.94,1:23:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}{\bord0\shad4\fs75\pos(958,898)}你做的不是很多
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.44,1:23:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你有病吗？\N{\fs60}Wait. Are you sick?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.35,1:23:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}艾滋病？\N{\fs60}SIDA? AIDS?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.91,1:23:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}问一问这个白人，他会知道答案的\N{\fs60}Ask the white man. He will know.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.24,1:23:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}先生，我的手会长回来吗？\N{\fs60}Sir, will my hand grow back?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.21,1:23:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}萨米昂？\N{\fs60}Simeon.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.46,1:23:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}记住，尤里，立场\N{\fs60}Remember, Yuri, take sides.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.30,1:24:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}萨米昂\N{\fs60}Simeon!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.01,1:24:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}他是安德烈的人 - 去他的安德烈\N{\fs60}Don't! He's Andre's.  - Fuck Andre!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.21,1:24:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}去他的安德烈\N{\fs60}Fuck Andre!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.84,1:24:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}对不起，这些枪平时不是这样的\N{\fs60}I'm sorry they don't usually do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.64,1:24:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}让我看一看，我也许可以把它修好\N{\fs60}Let me look it. Maybe I can fix it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.64,1:24:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}让我看一看，是弹夹的问题\N{\fs60}Let me see it. It's the magazine.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.24,1:24:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}给我看看\N{\fs60}Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.22,1:24:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}去你的\N{\fs60}Fuck you!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.59,1:24:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我开始觉得我被诅咒了\N{\fs60}I started to feel I'd been cursed.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.31,1:24:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}不死的诅咒\N{\fs60}...the curse of invincibility.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.84,1:25:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}尼奇，回到你的房间去\N{\fs60}Nicki, please, go to your room.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.60,1:25:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我不相信你\N{\fs60}I don't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.35,1:25:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你能证明这些吗？\N{\fs60}Can you prove any of this?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.15,1:25:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}奥洛夫先生花了很长时间\N{\fs60}Mr. Orlov goes to a lot of trouble
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.97,1:25:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}才使他的公司看起来像是做正当生意的\N{\fs60}to make his business look legitimate.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.01,1:25:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}即使是对你\N{\fs60}Even to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.34,1:25:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}特别是对你\N{\fs60}Perhaps especially to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.06,1:25:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我想我们今天在这里什么也不会发现\N{\fs60}I don't expect we'll find anything here today.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.02,1:25:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你到底想要什么？\N{\fs60}So what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.87,1:25:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我希望你可以帮助我\N{\fs60}I was hoping that you would help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.19,1:25:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我了解...\N{\fs60}I understand that uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.09,1:25:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你的父母的死很悲惨\N{\fs60}your parents died tragically?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.01,1:25:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}杀死你父母的枪械\N{\fs60}The illegal firearms used to murder your mother and father
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.32,1:25:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}是从像你丈夫那样的人那里来得\N{\fs60}were procured from men exactly like your husband.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.92,1:25:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我想你离开这里\N{\fs60}I'd like you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.16,1:26:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}好的，先生们\N{\fs60}Okay. Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.49,1:26:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}艾娃？\N{\fs60}Ava?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.35,1:26:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}艾娃，你怎么了？\N{\fs60}Ava, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.25,1:26:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我不能穿这些衣服\N{\fs60}I can't wear the clothes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.10,1:26:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我不能戴这些首饰\N{\fs60}Can't wear the jewelry.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.46,1:26:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我不能开车\N{\fs60}Can't drive the car.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.70,1:26:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我不能住在这间房子里\N{\fs60}Can't live in this house.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.88,1:26:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}所有的东西都沾满了鲜血\N{\fs60}Everything's got blood on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.83,1:26:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}沾满了鲜血？\N{\fs60}Blood on it?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.52,1:26:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你到底怎么了？\N{\fs60}What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.40,1:26:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}不要这么闹情绪\N{\fs60}Don't be so melodramatic.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.22,1:26:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我没不是在闹情绪\N{\fs60}I'm melodramatic.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.71,1:27:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我是个失败的演员，记得吗?\N{\fs60}I'm a failed actress, remember?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.73,1:27:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我告诉过你这些人有政治目的\N{\fs60}I told you, these people, it's political.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.53,1:27:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}他们在说谎，他们是说谎的人\N{\fs60}They lie. They're liars.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.55,1:27:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}看着我，他们用谎言来美化自己，知道吗?\N{\fs60}Look at me. They lie to make themselves look good, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.88,1:27:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你不能相信他们\N{\fs60}You can't trust them.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.72,1:27:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}不只是他们\N{\fs60}It's not just them.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.28,1:27:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}不用担心，你的家人什么也没说\N{\fs60}Don't worry. Your family didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.72,1:27:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}他们不需要这么做\N{\fs60}They didn't have to.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.47,1:27:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我卖给这些人力量去保护他们自己，艾娃\N{\fs60}I sell people a means to defend themselves. Ava.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.11,1:27:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我只做这些\N{\fs60}That's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.04,1:27:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}尤里，我看过新闻，我看过那些照片\N{\fs60}Yuri, I see the news. I see those pictures.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.15,1:27:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}那些枪比孩子们还要高!\N{\fs60}The guns are bigger than the boys!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.61,1:27:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我做的事没有一点是不合法的!\N{\fs60}There is nothing illegal about what I do!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.19,1:27:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我才不管它是否合法!\N{\fs60}I don't care if it's legal!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.79,1:27:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}那是不对的!\N{\fs60}It's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.94,1:28:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}求求你，收手吧\N{\fs60}Please, stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.00,1:28:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我干或不干已经没有区别了\N{\fs60}It makes no difference if I stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.97,1:28:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}第二天，就会有人接替我的位置\N{\fs60}Someone will take my place the next day.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.05,1:28:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}让他们去干吧，我们已经有足够的钱了\N{\fs60}So let them. We have enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.63,1:28:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}这并不是关于钱\N{\fs60}It's not about the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.38,1:28:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}那是关于什么？\N{\fs60}Then what is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.25,1:28:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我干这个很拿手\N{\fs60}I'm good at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.41,1:28:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我觉得我一生唯一所做的事就是长的漂亮\N{\fs60}I feel like all I've done my whole life is be pretty.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.39,1:28:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我的出世就已经成就了现在的我\N{\fs60}I mean all I've done is be born.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.05,1:28:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我是一个失败的演员，失败的艺术家\N{\fs60}I'm a failed actress, a failed artist.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.24,1:29:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}失败的妈妈\N{\fs60}I'm not much good as a mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.12,1:29:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我有时觉得自己甚至已不再美丽了\N{\fs60}I'm not even that pretty anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.31,1:29:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我什么事都已经失败了，尤里\N{\fs60}I have failed at everything, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.06,1:29:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}但我不能做一个失败的人\N{\fs60}But I won't fail as a human being.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.44,1:29:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我的敌人终于找到了一种可以伤害我的武器\N{\fs60}that could hurt me. My enemies had finally found a weapon
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.66,1:29:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}在接下来的6个月了\N{\fs60}For the next six months,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.87,1:29:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我不再走私枪支了\N{\fs60}I stopped running guns.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.03,1:29:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我开始做正当生意\N{\fs60}I went legitimate.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.22,1:29:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}这是一个不可限量的市场\N{\fs60}This is an untapped market.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.38,1:29:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我们在说5百万平方米的森林 仅仅是第一年\N{\fs60}I'm talking over five million cubic meters of timber in the first year alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.64,1:29:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}超过100种可以开发的种类\N{\fs60}Over 100 exploitable species.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.86,1:29:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}石油?\N{\fs60}The oil?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.01,1:29:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}只是在你和我之间\N{\fs60}Between you and me, this...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.29,1:29:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}1万桶一个月\N{\fs60}Ten thousand barrels a month?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.39,1:29:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}他一定是在说谎，他在说谎!\N{\fs60}He must be lying. He's talking!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.30,1:29:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}这有一些石油储备石油输出国组织根本不知道\N{\fs60}Listen, there are gas reserves off the lvory Coast that OPEC doesn't even know about.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.08,1:29:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}这些电话号码已经都检查过了\N{\fs60}The phone numbers all check out.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.03,1:29:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}都是合法的\N{\fs60}It's all on the level.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.87,1:30:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}怪不得瓦伦丁会困惑了\N{\fs60}No wonder Valentine was confused.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.14,1:30:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}感谢上帝\N{\fs60}Thank God there are still legal ways
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.94,1:30:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}还是有一些合法渠道可以和发展中国家交易\N{\fs60}to exploit developing countries.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.31,1:30:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}但是合法的钱\N{\fs60}The only problem with an honest buck
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.48,1:30:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}真是难赚\N{\fs60}is they're so hard to make.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.20,1:30:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}很多人都在干\N{\fs60}The margins are too low.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.91,1:30:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}利润实在太低了\N{\fs60}Too many people are doing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.58,1:30:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}但是我已经答应了艾娃\N{\fs60}Still, I'd promised Ava.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.73,1:30:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}尤里，利比里亚的总统正在来这里的路\N{\fs60}Yuri, the President of Liberia is on his way up.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.04,1:30:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}他早到了\N{\fs60}He's early.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.30,1:30:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我一会就回来\N{\fs60}I'll be back in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.82,1:31:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你来这做什么，安德烈?\N{\fs60}What the fuck are you doing here, Andre?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.16,1:31:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我到联合国来签和平条约\N{\fs60}We are here for peace talks at the United Nations.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.31,1:31:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}所以你决定顺便来问候你的军火商?\N{\fs60}So at the same time you thought you'd drop in on your arms dealer?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.74,1:31:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我只是奇怪那还是你的职业吗?\N{\fs60}Well, I was beginning to wonder whether that was still your profession.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.35,1:31:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你要知道你这个人并不好找\N{\fs60}You know, you're a hard man to get a hold of all of Sudden.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.65,1:31:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}太可惜了\N{\fs60}That is a shame.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.41,1:31:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我儿子和我准备在纽约\N{\fs60}My son and I were hoping to do a little shopping.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.17,1:31:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}顺道购物一番\N{\fs60}While in New York.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.55,1:31:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}他们在监视你，你知道吗？\N{\fs60}You know they're watching you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.77,1:31:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}是的，我知道\N{\fs60}Yes, I know they blame me.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.58,1:31:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}他们什么事都要怪在我头上 那些伪君子!\N{\fs60}They blame me for everything, those hypocrites.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.03,1:31:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}他们在找一个巫师(政治迫害的错误语法)\N{\fs60}There're hunt for a witch.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.03,1:31:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}{\an7\fs70\bord0\shad2}巫师（witch hunt)：政治迫害的错误语法)
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.95,1:31:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}是政治迫害\N{\fs60}Witch hunt.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.29,1:31:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}冲突已经升级了\N{\fs60}Hostilities have escalated.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.98,1:31:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我无法得到我想要的资源\N{\fs60}And they are making it very difficult for me to re-supply.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.26,1:31:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}这需要一个像你这样的人来协调\N{\fs60}That requires a man of your rare ingenuity.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.90,1:31:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}对不起，我无法帮助你\N{\fs60}I can't help you, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.70,1:31:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我理解\N{\fs60}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.88,1:31:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}但是你应该知道这些:\N{\fs60}But you should know this:
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.85,1:31:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}在目前的情况下\N{\fs60}Due to our present situation
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.55,1:32:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我们愿意付出任何代价\N{\fs60}we are compelled to be unusually generous.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.53,1:32:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}希望很快见到你，战争之王\N{\fs60}So, see you soon, Lord of War.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.51,1:32:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你还没有给我兰博之枪\N{\fs60}You still haven't brought me the gun of Rambo.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.33,1:32:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}一个四个半月大的胎儿\N{\fs60}At four and a half months old...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.21,1:32:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}可以看到尾骨\N{\fs60}a human fetus has a reptile's tail...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.19,1:32:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}这就是进化的证明\N{\fs60}a remnant of our evolution.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.24,1:32:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}也许那就是我无法停止的原因\N{\fs60}Maybe that's what I couldn't escape.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.45,1:32:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你可以和许多敌人战斗过 仍然存活下来\N{\fs60}You can fight a lot of enemies and survive,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.88,1:32:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}但是如果你和你自己战斗\N{\fs60}but if you fight your biology,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.79,1:32:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你总是会输\N{\fs60}you always lose.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.17,1:32:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你们不要和我说再见吗？\N{\fs60}You guys aren't waiting to say goodbye?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.76,1:32:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我还要10分钟才离开这里\N{\fs60}I'm not leaving for another ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.09,1:32:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}对不起，尼奇要去上游泳课了\N{\fs60}Sorry, Nicki has swim practice.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.27,1:32:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我知道你要出差，我觉的很高兴\N{\fs60}You know, I'm kind of glad you're going.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.29,1:33:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你在这里呆的太久 我开始有些担心了\N{\fs60}You've been here so long you're starting to get on my nerves.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.18,1:33:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}这个石油项目会在周四结束\N{\fs60}This oil concession should be wrapped up by Thursday.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.55,1:33:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}周末我就会回来\N{\fs60}I'll be back for the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.72,1:33:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我们一家人出去聚一聚\N{\fs60}We'll go somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.79,1:33:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}去海边\N{\fs60}The sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.86,1:33:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}那太好了\N{\fs60}That would be fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.12,1:33:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}好\N{\fs60}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.95,1:33:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你相信我，对吗？\N{\fs60}Hey. You trust me, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.30,1:33:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}她看着我的眼神\N{\fs60}She looked me directly in the eye...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.06,1:33:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}就像我看着上千名海关人员，政府官员\N{\fs60}the way I've looked in the eyes of a thousand customs officials...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.80,1:33:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}和其他执法官员的眼神一样\N{\fs60}government bureaucrats and law enforcement agents.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.41,1:33:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}是的，我相信你\N{\fs60}Yes, I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.73,1:33:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}她就这样向我撒了慌\N{\fs60}And she lied without flinching.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.25,1:33:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}再见，宝贝\N{\fs60}I'll see you, big guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.28,1:33:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}再见，爸爸\N{\fs60}Bye Papa.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.05,1:33:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}她从最好的人那里学到了这些\N{\fs60}She learned from the best.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.75,1:33:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}祝你旅行愉快\N{\fs60}Have a good trip.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.27,1:33:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}那就是他\N{\fs60}That's him.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.03,1:34:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我们要去哪里，妈妈？\N{\fs60}Where are we going, Mama?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.96,1:34:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}这是一个游戏，亲爱的\N{\fs60}It's a game, honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.16,1:34:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}像捉迷藏一样吗？\N{\fs60}Like hide and seek?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.58,1:34:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}是的\N{\fs60}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.29,1:34:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}像捉迷藏一样\N{\fs60}Like hide and seek.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.78,1:34:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}如果我被跟踪了，我总是会感觉到\N{\fs60}I can always sense when I'm being tailed.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.08,1:34:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我知道怎样找到被跟踪的迹像\N{\fs60}I know what to look for.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.86,1:34:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}但是我从来没有被我爱的女人跟踪过\N{\fs60}But then I'd never been tailed by the woman I love.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.21,1:35:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我可以了解她在想什么\N{\fs60}I can put myself in Ava's place.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.82,1:35:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}她猜到密码也许是我的社安号的最后4位\N{\fs60}She might've understood if the combination was the last four digits of my social security number...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.13,1:35:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我的生日，或者是她的生日\N{\fs60}my birth date, even her birth date,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.69,1:35:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}但是她不会猜到是尼克的生日\N{\fs60}but not Nicolai's.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.31,1:35:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我儿子的生日打开了它\N{\fs60}My son's birthday unlocked
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.95,1:35:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}政府后来称它为"武器大全"\N{\fs60}what the government would later describe as "a catalogue of carnage."
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.72,1:35:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你要呆在这里\N{\fs60}Nicki, stay right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.82,1:36:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我们走，尼克\N{\fs60}Come on, Nicki.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.18,1:37:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}来看我们怎么赔钱吗？\N{\fs60}Come to see how the other half lives?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.01,1:37:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我想念你做的菜\N{\fs60}I miss your borscht.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.91,1:37:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}爸爸妈妈告诉我你成功戒毒了\N{\fs60}Mom and Dad say you're clean.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.47,1:37:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}是的，你不也是吗\N{\fs60}Yeah, you, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.11,1:37:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你开始做正当生意了?\N{\fs60}You went legit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.44,1:37:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}真是不敢相信\N{\fs60}That's hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.87,1:37:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}那是因为那不是真的\N{\fs60}That's because it's not true.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.86,1:37:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}只有你知道\N{\fs60}Only you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.96,1:37:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我今晚要离开，有生意要做\N{\fs60}I'm leaving tonight on a job
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.71,1:37:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我想让你和我一起去\N{\fs60}I want you to come.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.62,1:37:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我不能去，我有了女朋友\N{\fs60}I can't. I've got a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.99,1:37:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我想她就是我想要结婚的人\N{\fs60}I think she might be the one.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.51,1:37:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}而且我想自己开一家餐馆\N{\fs60}Plus, I'm thinking of opening my own place.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.30,1:37:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}这次的生意也许可以帮助你\N{\fs60}Maybe this trip will help.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.05,1:37:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}可以赚很多钱\N{\fs60}It's good money.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.95,1:37:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}尤里，我已经同他们发誓不再干了\N{\fs60}Yuri, I've given my word.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.30,1:37:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}没有人会知道\N{\fs60}No one has to know.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.05,1:37:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我告诉他们我们去做石油生意\N{\fs60}Tell them we going for a little R and R.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.56,1:37:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}为什么你突然开始需要我了?\N{\fs60}What do you need me for, all of sudden?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.34,1:37:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}西非现在很混乱\N{\fs60}West Africa's fucked up.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.81,1:37:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}不同往日的\N{\fs60}More than usual.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.16,1:38:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我没有任何人可以相信\N{\fs60}I can't trust anybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.10,1:38:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我需要你保护我\N{\fs60}I need you to watch my back.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.03,1:38:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}{\bord0\shad4\fs75\pos(936,900.7)}兄弟心连心
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.29,1:38:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}{\bord0\shad4\fad(400,300)\fs75\pos(444,906.1)}利比里亚首都，蒙罗维亚 - 2001
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.78,1:38:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}尤里!欢迎你回来\N{\fs60}Yuri! Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.44,1:38:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}欢迎你们两个人\N{\fs60}Welcome both of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.22,1:38:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}欢迎来到民主国家\N{\fs60}Welcome to democracy.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.11,1:38:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}民主国家？\N{\fs60}Democracy?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.24,1:38:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你最近到底喝了什么？安迪\N{\fs60}What have you been drinking, Andy?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.82,1:39:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你看新闻了吗?\N{\fs60}Huh, you have not seen the news.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.74,1:39:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}他们控告我非法操纵大选\N{\fs60}You know they accuse me of rigging elections.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.18,1:39:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}但是在你们最高法院 对于佛罗里达的事作出最后判决后\N{\fs60}But after this, with your Florida and you Supreme Court of Kangaroos,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.74,1:39:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}美国要永远的闭嘴了\N{\fs60}Now, the U.S. Must shut up forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.44,1:39:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你是怎么办到的，尤里?\N{\fs60}How do you do this, Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.76,1:39:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你是如何\N{\fs60}How do you do this,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.50,1:39:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}在他们监视着我领空的条件下办到的?\N{\fs60}when they are watching all of my airspace?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.71,1:39:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}哪里有需求，哪里就会有武器\N{\fs60}Where there's a will, there's a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.06,1:39:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}快点，我的钱在哪？\N{\fs60}Come on, where's my fucking money?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.48,1:39:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你把货送到后，你就会收到钱\N{\fs60}When it is delivered.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.99,1:39:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}货已经送到了\N{\fs60}It is delivered.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.15,1:39:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}这些货不是给我的\N{\fs60}This is not for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.88,1:39:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}它是给我西面的邻居的\N{\fs60}This is for my neighbors to the west.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.24,1:39:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}西边?\N{\fs60}The west?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.91,1:39:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我们要去塞拉利昂\N{\fs60}We're going to Sierra Leone.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.54,1:39:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}没错，我的儿子安德烈二世\N{\fs60}Oh, yes. And my son Baptiste Junior
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.16,1:39:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}会和你们一起去帮你们作介绍\N{\fs60}will go with you to make the proper introductions.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.29,1:39:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我们没有卡车\N{\fs60}We have no trucks.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.46,1:39:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你们会有的\N{\fs60}You will.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.63,1:40:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我们运完食物后，你们就有卡车了\N{\fs60}As soon as we get the food out of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.91,1:40:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}兰博之枪\N{\fs60}Gun of Rambo.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.00,1:40:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}尤里先生，你很守信用\N{\fs60}Mr. Yuri, you're a man of your word.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.43,1:40:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我们去哪里？\N{\fs60}So where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.15,1:40:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}RUF，自由战士\N{\fs60}RUF -the Freedom Fighters.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.66,1:40:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}每一个在非洲的派系 喜欢给自己起一些高尚的名字\N{\fs60}Every faction in Africa calls themselves by the noble names.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.46,1:40:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}解放这个，爱国那个\N{\fs60}Liberation-this Patriotic-that,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.54,1:40:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}或者共和或民主什么的\N{\fs60}Democratic Republic of-something-or-other.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.47,1:40:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}也许他们不知道自己是什么\N{\fs60}I guess they can't own up to what they usually are
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.15,1:40:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}地球唯一喜欢战争的民族\N{\fs60}Federation of Worse Oppressors than the Last Bunch of Oppressors.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.54,1:40:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}往往最残忍的暴行\N{\fs60}Often, the most barbaric atrocities occur
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.54,1:40:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}都出自声称自己为自由战士的人们\N{\fs60}when both combatants proclaim themselves "freedom fighters."
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.04,1:40:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}好的，我有500支枪，全新的\N{\fs60}Right, I've got 500 units, brand new right out of the box,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.21,1:40:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}刚刚从箱子里拿出来，都和这支一样新\N{\fs60}all as clean as this. What have you got?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.43,1:41:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}上帝啊\N{\fs60}God! Oh, Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.89,1:41:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}上帝啊\N{\fs60}God! Oh, Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.81,1:41:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}尤里，我要和你谈一谈\N{\fs60}Yuri, I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.09,1:41:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}现在不可以\N{\fs60}Not now.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.20,1:41:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}现在就要\N{\fs60}Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.25,1:41:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}对不起，失陪一下\N{\fs60}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.39,1:41:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}怎么了?\N{\fs60}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.65,1:41:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我们不能做这笔交易!\N{\fs60}We can't do this deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.25,1:41:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你到底怎么了？\N{\fs60}The fuck we can't! What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.99,1:41:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}看那边\N{\fs60}Look, over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.58,1:41:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}当我们把枪交给他们的时候 那些人就会被杀!\N{\fs60}As soon as we hand over the guns those people are going to die!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.71,1:41:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}那不关我们的事\N{\fs60}It's not our business.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.98,1:42:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}他们刚刚杀了一个和尼克相同年纪的小孩\N{\fs60}They killed a boy just now as young as Nicki.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.66,1:42:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}有什么问题吗？\N{\fs60}What is the holdup?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.36,1:42:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}没有问题\N{\fs60}There is no holdup.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.56,1:42:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我马上就过去\N{\fs60}I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.26,1:42:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}维塔利，我们一直知道这个事实\N{\fs60}Vitaly, it's what we always know:
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.01,1:42:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我们不能控制他们要干什么\N{\fs60}We can't control what they do.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.86,1:42:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}不，尤里，今天我们可以\N{\fs60}No, no, today we can. Today we can.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.45,1:42:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}他们就在那里!\N{\fs60}Yuri, they're right there!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.90,1:42:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}如果我们真这么做的话\N{\fs60}What do you think they'll do to us if we back out?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.10,1:42:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}他们会杀了我们\N{\fs60}They'll kill us.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.21,1:42:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}但是我们继续 你知道他们会怎样对这些人吗？\N{\fs60}And if we go ahead, what do you think they'll do to them?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.71,1:42:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我们要做些事帮助他们\N{\fs60}We've got to do something.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.54,1:42:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}{\bord0\shad4\fs75\pos(936,900.7)}求你了，看在上帝的份上
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.46,1:42:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}{\bord0\shad4\fs75\pos(950,900.7)}这不是我们的战争
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.88,1:42:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}{\bord0\shad4\fs75\pos(936,900.7)}求你了，兄弟心连心
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.90,1:42:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}他在说什么？\N{\fs60}What is he saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.55,1:42:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}是交易\N{\fs60}It's the deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.76,1:42:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我的弟弟对交易的一些细节不满\N{\fs60}My brother's not happy with the terms.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.46,1:42:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我们在讨论这个问题，没事的\N{\fs60}We'll work it out. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.81,1:42:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}对不对，没事的\N{\fs60}Right? It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.33,1:43:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}没事的\N{\fs60}Yeah. Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.20,1:43:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}尤里，你说的没错\N{\fs60}You're right. Yuri, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.29,1:43:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}上帝啊，我脑子一定出问题了\N{\fs60}God, I've got to get my shit together.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.80,1:43:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}这不是我们的战争\N{\fs60}This is not our fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.53,1:43:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}没错\N{\fs60}Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.88,1:43:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}交易内容是什么来着？\N{\fs60}Okay. What's the deal?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.62,1:43:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}300支肩抗式火箭筒 500支步枪，800枚手榴弹\N{\fs60}300 RPGs, 500 assault rifles and 800 grenades.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.98,1:43:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我以为是1200枚手榴弹\N{\fs60}I thought it was 1200 grenades.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.63,1:43:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我太重视这次交易了\N{\fs60}I was so caught up in the deal...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.37,1:43:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我没有仔细思考过维塔利的脑子里到底在想什么\N{\fs60}I never realized what was going on in Vitaly's head.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.10,1:43:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我以为是1200枚手榴弹\N{\fs60}I thought it was 1200 grenades.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.91,1:43:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我记错了\N{\fs60}Confused.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.95,1:43:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}再回头想想\N{\fs60}Come to think about it,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.90,1:43:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}也许我永远也不会知道他脑子里在想什么\N{\fs60}maybe I never understood what was going on in his head.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.14,1:43:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}对不起\N{\fs60}I beg your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.70,1:43:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我可以看一看另一颗钻石吗？\N{\fs60}May I see another stone?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.42,1:43:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}有一点我很确定\N{\fs60}One thing I do understand for certain...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.34,1:44:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}就是维塔利打破了走私枪支最重要的规则\N{\fs60}is that Vitaly broke the cardinal rule of gunrunning.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.86,1:44:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}永远不要拿起一支枪 变成和你客户一样的人\N{\fs60}Never pick up a gun and join the customers.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.82,1:44:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你在干什么？\N{\fs60}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.20,1:44:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}为尤里做一些事\N{\fs60}Something for Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.98,1:44:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}放下它，慢慢的\N{\fs60}Step away. Slow.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.83,1:44:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}不要，维塔利\N{\fs60}No, Vit!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.62,1:44:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}不要，维塔利\N{\fs60}No! Vit!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.15,1:46:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}只有一半的枪支被炸毁了\N{\fs60}Only half the guns were gone...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.06,1:46:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}所以我依然得到了一半的钻石\N{\fs60}so I was still entitled to half the diamonds.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.35,1:46:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}如果我拿了它们，我失去了一些东西\N{\fs60}If I took them, I was lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.66,1:46:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}如果我不拿它们，我也是失去了一些东西\N{\fs60}If I left them, I was lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.27,1:46:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}一场大屠杀发生了，就像维塔利所说的那样\N{\fs60}The massacre played out exactly how Vitaly predicted.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.64,1:46:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}另外，那一周在塞拉利昂\N{\fs60}But then, a half-dozen other massacres
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.54,1:46:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}还发生了许多大屠杀\N{\fs60}happened in Sierra Leone that week.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.12,1:46:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你不可能制止所有的大屠杀\N{\fs60}You can't stop them all.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.82,1:46:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}以我的经验来说 你不可能制止任何一个大屠杀\N{\fs60}In my experience, you can't stop any of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.36,1:46:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}人们说 “如果正义之士不行动的话，邪恶就获胜了”\N{\fs60}They say evil prevails when good men fail to act.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.23,1:46:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}这句话应该是，“邪恶获胜了”\N{\fs60}What they ought to say is, evil prevails.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.06,1:47:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我现在和被上帝遗忘的这个国家的统治者\N{\fs60}I now shared even more in common...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.17,1:47:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}有了更多的相同点\N{\fs60}with the leader of that country God seemed to have forsaken.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.51,1:47:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我们在对方里看到了一些我们并不喜欢的东西\N{\fs60}We saw something in each other that neither of us liked.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.85,1:47:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}也许我们各自只是在看一面镜子\N{\fs60}Or maybe we were just looking in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.49,1:47:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我给了一个利比里亚医生20美元\N{\fs60}I paid a Monrovian doctor twenty dollars
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.90,1:47:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}叫他把维塔利身体里的子弹都取出来\N{\fs60}to remove the lead from Vitaly's body
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.81,1:47:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}然后写一个伪造的死亡证明书\N{\fs60}and write a bogus death certificate.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.74,1:47:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我应该多给他一些\N{\fs60}I should've paid more.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.66,1:47:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我走私里上百万的弹药\N{\fs60}I've smuggled millions of rounds of ammunition,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.14,1:47:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}但是那颗把我送到监狱里的\N{\fs60}and the bullet that lands me in jail...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.88,1:47:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}确是那颗在我弟弟肋骨下的子弹\N{\fs60}is found under my dead brother's rib.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.97,1:47:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}尤里·奥洛夫\N{\fs60}Yuri Orlov.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.96,1:47:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我是美国烟酒枪械管理署的\N{\fs60}We're with the Bureau of Alcohol, Tobacco, and Firearms.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.96,1:48:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}让我猜一猜\N{\fs60}Let me guess.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.10,1:48:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}这一定不是关于烟和酒\N{\fs60}This is not about the alcohol or the tobacco.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:44.39,1:48:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}克里米亚餐馆\N{\fs60}Crimean Restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.82,1:48:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}爸爸？\N{\fs60}Papa?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.25,1:48:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我两个儿子都已经死了\N{\fs60}Both my sons are dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.89,1:49:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}生活中有两种悲惨的事\N{\fs60}There are only two tragedies in life.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.61,1:49:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}一种是你想要的得不到\N{\fs60}One is not getting what you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.96,1:49:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}另一种是你得到了\N{\fs60}The other is getting it.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.42,1:49:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}这是不是你的？\N{\fs60}Is this one of yours?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.67,1:49:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}杰克·范伦提终于得到了他想要的\N{\fs60}Jack Valentine finally had what he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:10.58,1:49:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}真奇怪，死亡证明书上写他死于心脏衰竭\N{\fs60}Curiously, the death certificate says he died of heart failure.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.09,1:49:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}伪造死亡证明书？\N{\fs60}Falsifying a death certificate?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.47,1:49:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}这个罪名可告不了我\N{\fs60}That's not gonna hold me.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.47,1:49:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你说的没错 和平时一样，你又说对了\N{\fs60}You're right. As usual, you are right.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.67,1:49:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你看今天的报纸了吗？\N{\fs60}Have you seen today's paper? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.22,1:49:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}假冒使用者证明书\N{\fs60}Fake end-user certificates.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:38.02,1:49:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}空壳公司，虚假目录\N{\fs60}Cut-out companies, meticulously catalogued.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.24,1:49:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}世界上没有一个独裁者\N{\fs60}There is hardly a warlord, dictator, despot anywhere in the world
Dialogue: 0,1:49:45.66,1:49:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}军阀没有和你打过交道\N{\fs60}that you're a first-name basis with.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.08,1:49:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}是你的妻子帮助，让我们捉到了你\N{\fs60}It was your wife your trophy wife that led us to the prize.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.88,1:49:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}那不是她的错\N{\fs60}It's not her fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.85,1:49:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}她只是比你好跟踪罢了\N{\fs60}She's just easier to follow than you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:58.77,1:49:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我可以看报纸吗？\N{\fs60}May I?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.56,1:50:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}没问题，看吧\N{\fs60}Yeah, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.74,1:50:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}慢慢享受吧\N{\fs60}Enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.89,1:50:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}什么？\N{\fs60}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.79,1:50:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}这个\N{\fs60}This.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.47,1:50:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}随你说吧\N{\fs60}Tell me I'm everything you despise.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:33.98,1:50:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}说我是邪恶的化身\N{\fs60}That I'm the personification of evil.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.46,1:50:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}还有什么?\N{\fs60}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.73,1:50:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}应该对世界混乱的秩序负责\N{\fs60}Responsible for the breakdown of the fabric of society and world order.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.54,1:50:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}创造大屠杀的人\N{\fs60}I'm a one-man genocide.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.26,1:50:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你现在想说什么就说什么吧\N{\fs60}Say everything you want to say to me now.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.09,1:50:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}因为你已经没时间了\N{\fs60}Because you don't have long.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.12,1:50:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你在注意听吗?\N{\fs60}Are you paying attention?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.70,1:50:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}还是你在做梦?\N{\fs60}Or are you delusional?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:55.23,1:50:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你已经违反了每一条法律\N{\fs60}You have broken every arms embargo written.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.82,1:51:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我们有足够的证据来判你终身监禁\N{\fs60}There is enough here to put you away for consecutive life sentences.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.22,1:51:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}在你真正进监狱之前\N{\fs60}You are going to spend the next ten years of your life
Dialogue: 0,1:51:05.19,1:51:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你会花十年时间\N{\fs60}going from a cell to a courtroom
Dialogue: 0,1:51:07.18,1:51:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}在监狱和法院之间穿梭\N{\fs60} before you even start serving your time.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:12.68,1:51:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我想你没有真正认识到这个问题的严重性\N{\fs60}I don't think you fully appreciate the seriousness of your situation.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.05,1:51:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我的家人不认我了\N{\fs60}My family has disowned me.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.38,1:51:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我的妻子和孩子离开了我\N{\fs60}My wife and son have left me.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.10,1:51:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我的弟弟死了\N{\fs60}My brother's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:39.59,1:51:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}相信我\N{\fs60}Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:41.14,1:51:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我很真正认识到这个问题的严重性\N{\fs60}I fully appreciate the seriousness of my situation.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.99,1:51:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我敢对你发誓\N{\fs60}But I promise you,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:47.17,1:51:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我不会在法院里呆上一秒钟\N{\fs60}I won't spend a single second in a courtroom.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:51.07,1:51:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你是在做梦\N{\fs60}You are delusional.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.30,1:51:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我喜欢你杰克\N{\fs60}I like you, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:55.66,1:51:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}不，也许不是，但是我了解你\N{\fs60}Well, maybe not, but I understand you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:02.90,1:52:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}让我来告诉你将会发生什么\N{\fs60}Let me tell you what's gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.15,1:52:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}这样可以让你有所准备\N{\fs60}This way, you can prepare yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:13.07,1:52:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}好的\N{\fs60}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.42,1:52:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}很快，会有人来敲门\N{\fs60}Soon there's going to be a knock on that door
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.58,1:52:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你会被叫到外面去\N{\fs60}and you will be called outside.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:17.91,1:52:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}在过道里 会有一个官阶比你高的人站在那里\N{\fs60}In the hall there will be a man who outranks you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:20.46,1:52:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}首先，他会祝贺你所做的一切\N{\fs60}First, he'll compliment you on the fine job you've done
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.63,1:52:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你使世界成为一个和平的地方\N{\fs60}that you're making the world a safer place
Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.11,1:52:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你会得到奖状或升职\N{\fs60}that you're to receive a commendation and a promotion.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.60,1:52:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}然后他会告诉你，我需要被释放\N{\fs60}And then he'll tell you that I am to be released.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.41,1:52:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你会反对\N{\fs60}You're gonna protest.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:35.86,1:52:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你也许会以辞职来要挟他\N{\fs60}You'll probably threaten to resign.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.93,1:52:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}但是在最后，我会被释放\N{\fs60}But in the end, I will be released.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.10,1:52:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我被释放的原因\N{\fs60}The reason I'll be released
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.52,1:52:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}和你认为我会被判刑的原因是一样的\N{\fs60}is the same reason you think I'll be convicted.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:46.76,1:52:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我和一些世界上\N{\fs60}I do rub shoulders with some of the most vile,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.70,1:52:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}称自己为领导人的人打交道\N{\fs60}sadistic men calling themselves leaders today.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.00,1:53:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}这些人当中的有一些人是你的敌人的敌人\N{\fs60}But some of those men are the enemies of your enemies.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:01.44,1:53:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}世界上最大的军火交易商是你的老板\N{\fs60}And while the biggest arms dealer in the world is your boss...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.53,1:53:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}美国的总统\N{\fs60}the President of the United States,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.70,1:53:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}他一天卖的比我一年卖的还多\N{\fs60}who ships more merchandise in a day I do in a year
Dialogue: 0,1:53:12.42,1:53:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}有时 在枪支上找到他的指纹是一件很尴尬的事\N{\fs60}sometimes it's embarrassing to have his fingerprints on the guns.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.09,1:53:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}有时，他需要像我这样的自由工作者\N{\fs60}Sometimes he needs a freelancer like me
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.16,1:53:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}来支持那些他不可能支持的军队\N{\fs60}to supply forces he can't be seen supplying.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.17,1:53:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}所以\N{\fs60}So
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.94,1:53:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你称我为恶魔\N{\fs60}you call me evil,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:29.83,1:53:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}但不幸的是\N{\fs60}but unfortunately for you
Dialogue: 0,1:53:32.54,1:53:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我是一个必须要存在的恶魔\N{\fs60}I'm a necessary evil.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:50.55,1:53:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我会告诉你去下地狱\N{\fs60}I would tell you to go to hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.06,1:53:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}但是我想你已经在那里了\N{\fs60}But I think you're already there.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:30.71,1:54:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}很高兴和你合作\N{\fs60}Pleasure doing business with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:33.09,1:54:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}对于很多人来说 离开监狱是一件很高兴的事\N{\fs60}Most people are happy just to get out of jail.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.49,1:54:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我不但离开监狱，还得到了钱\N{\fs60}I expect to be paid to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:38.36,1:54:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我不是一个傻瓜\N{\fs60}I'm not a fool.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.67,1:54:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}我知道他们在今天需要我\N{\fs60}I know that just because they needed me that day
Dialogue: 0,1:54:41.85,1:54:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}并不意味着明天会是一样的结果\N{\fs60}didn't mean they wouldn't make me a scapegoat the next.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:44.62,1:54:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}但是，我回去了\N{\fs60}But I was back,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.34,1:54:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}去做我最拿手的事\N{\fs60}doing what I do best.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:49.02,1:54:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}{\bord0\shad4\fs75\pos(950,906.1)}运雨伞到撒哈拉沙漠?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:51.07,1:54:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}{\bord0\shad4\fs75\pos(950,906.1)}遮阳伞
Dialogue: 0,1:55:10.88,1:55:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}你知道是谁会继承地球?\N{\fs60}You know who's going to inherit the Earth?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:13.67,1:55:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}军火商\N{\fs60}Arms dealers.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:15.25,1:55:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}因为其他人都在忙于相互残杀\N{\fs60}Because everyone else is too busy killing each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:18.77,1:55:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}生存的秘诀在于\N{\fs60}That's the secret to survival.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.04,1:55:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}永远不要加入战争\N{\fs60}Never go to war.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:25.94,1:55:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}特别与你自己\N{\fs60}Especially with yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:37.57,1:55:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}{\fad(600,600)\bord0\shad4\fs75\pos(948,692.8)}本片根据真实事件改编
Dialogue: 0,1:55:43.45,1:55:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}{\fad(600,600)\bord0\shad4\fs75\pos(956,906.1)}当私人枪支走私继续茁壮成长时\N世界上最大的军火供应商仍然是\N美国 英国 俄罗斯 法国 中国
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.25,1:55:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}{\fad(600,600)\bord0\shad4\fs75\pos(956,711.7)}五个联合国安全理事会常任理事国

